subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: Sixteen-year-old Alexis Thompson shot a five-under-par 67 on Saturday to share the lead with Song-Hee Kim of South Korea heading into the final round of the Avnet L.P.G.A. Classic in Mobile, Ala.
